      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr/>

  <div class="row home-content">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-justify">
      <h2 id="about">Testimonials</h2>
      <blockquote>
        “I have used Green Team Landscaping (or the prior same-owned company) since 2008, for both my private residence and investment property. I have been extremely pleased. They are prompt, polite, meticulous, honest and reasonably priced. It would be hard to do better!” – Marsha R., Wallingford
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        “Their customer service and quality of work is second to none. The Green Team is an absolute pleasure to do business with.” – Don K., Media
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        “We have been using the Green Team to service our property for over 10 years. We have recommended them to countless friends and family and would recommend them to anyone seeking professional landscaping.” – Michael and Mary H., Wallingford
      </blockquote>
      <blockquote>
        “Chris, the owner, is a great guy. He and his crew always show up on the scheduled day of service and never disappoint.” – Tony S., Glenolden
      </blockquote>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr/>

  <div class="row home-content">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-justify">
      <h2 id="services">Services</h2>
      <p>Here are our most popular services. Do you need something not listed? No worries, we do it all. Just contact us and ask.</p>

      <div class="well text-left" id="fullServiceButton">
        FULL SERVICE PROPERTY MAINTENANCE
        <div id="fullService" style="display: none;">
          <hr/>
          <%= image_tag 'full_service.jpg', class: 'img-responsive' %>
        </div>
      </div>
