    </div>
  </div>
  <hr/>

  <div class="row home-content">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-justify">
      <h2 id="whyus">Why Us?</h2>
      <p>
        Life is hectic, you're busy, we get it. That's why we want to help make your life a little bit easier. You pay for just about everything else online, why not your landscaping too? We are the first completely paperless invoicing landscaping team in Delaware County. We'll invoice you the day a service is provided. All you need to do is open your email and click "Pay Now” and a confirmation email will be sent instantly. Just to be sure we'll send you a monthly statement too so you can review your activity.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <hr/>

  <div class="row home-content">
    <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-6 col-md-offset-3 text-justify">
      <h2 id="team">The Team</h2>
      <p>
        Brian and Chris, both graduates of Strath Haven High School, formed a small landscaping company in 9th grade. They worked together until parting ways after graduation.  10 years later they teamed up again to pioneer a new kind of landscaping company, a professional enterprise that emphasizes customer service above all else.  The Green Team still delivers outstanding quality but it’s a happy customer that we strive for.
      </p>
      <br>
      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-xs-6 col-xs-offset-3 col-md-4 col-md-offset-1 text-center">
